TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a1 = random(2,5,1);
$b1 = random(2,5,1);
$c1 = random(2,5,1);
$d1 = random(2,5,1);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
$BR
Let \(f(x) = $a1 x + $b1 \) and \(g(x) = $c1 x^2 + $d1 x \).
$BR
After simplifying, 
$BR
\( (f \circ g)(x ) = \) \{ ans_rule(30)\}
EOT

$a3 = $a1*$c1;
$b3 = $a1*$d1;
$c3 = $b1  ;
$ans = "$a3*x**2 + $b3*x + $c3";

ANS(fun_cmp($ans));
